trans-unit.source: Provides the implementation for the server channel sink provider that creates <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink" /> instances.
trans-unit.target: Fornece a implementação do provedor de coletor de canal do servidor que cria instâncias de <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink> is used to create Web Services Description Language (WSDL) schema in situations where the URL ends with the string "?wsdl", for example, http://localhost/longbeard?wsdl.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSink> é usado para criar o esquema de WSDL Web Services Description Language () em situações onde a URL termina com a cadeia de caracteres "? wsdl", por exemplo, http://localhost/longbeard?wsdl.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" /> class with default values.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" /> com valores padrão.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> of configuration properties to use with the new instance of <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> de propriedades de configuração a ser usado com a nova instância de <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> of <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.SinkProviderData" /> instances to use with the new instance of <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BinaryServerFormatterSinkProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> de instâncias de <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.SinkProviderData" /> a ser usado com a nova instância de <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BinaryServerFormatterSinkProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" /> class with specified properties and provider data.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.SdlChannelSinkProvider" /> com as propriedades e os dados de provedor especificados.

trans-unit.source: The channel for which to create the channel sink chain.
trans-unit.target: O canal para o qual criar a cadeia de coletores de canal.

trans-unit.source: The first sink of the newly formed channel sink chain.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro coletor da cadeia de coletores de canal recém-formada.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IChannelDataStore" /> object in which the channel data is to be returned.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IChannelDataStore" /> no qual os dados de canal devem ser retornados.

trans-unit.source: Returns the channel data for the channel that the current sink is associated with.
trans-unit.target: Retorna os dados de canal para o canal ao qual o coletor atual está associado.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the next <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider" /> in the sink provider chain.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o próximo <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider" /> na cadeia de provedores de coletor.

trans-unit.source: The next <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider" /> in the sink provider chain.
trans-unit.target: A próxima <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IServerChannelSinkProvider" /> na cadeia de provedor de coletor.
